headline: Charles River Laboratories (CRL) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of lab services company Charles River Laboratories (NYSE:CRL) jumped 2.6% in the afternoon session after the stock's positive momentum continued, as Barclays upgraded the company to Overweight from Equal Weight and raised its price target.
